OL,3,CHosepipe ban: What you need to know as
OL,4,Chot weather leads to restrictions
OL,6,FA hosepipe ban has been introduced for
OL,7,Faround 850,000 customers in Kent "with
OL,8,Fimmediate effect", while millions of
OL,9,Fother UK households have been warned
OL,10,Fabout their water usage.
OL,12,FSouth East Water said the restrictions
OL,13,Fwill be officially enforced on Friday
OL,14,Fdue to the record heatwave gripping
OL,15,Fthe country.
OL,26,@oD@bOUpD@QO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/15
