OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1782442073
OL,3,CHosepipe ban: What you need to know as
OL,4,Chot weather leads to restrictions
OL,6,FIn an announcement on its website, the
OL,7,Ffirm said people should not use
OL,8,Fhosepipes for watering their gardens
OL,9,For washing cars, patios and boats, and
OL,10,Fmust refrain from filling swimming and
OL,11,Fpaddling pools.
OL,13,FIt comes after the Met Office issued a
OL,14,Fred weather warning for extreme heat,
OL,15,Fwhich has been extended until Friday
OL,16,Fand covers London and south-east
OL,17,FEngland, including Kent.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/15
