OL,3,CHosepipe ban: What you need to know as
OL,4,Chot weather leads to restrictions
OL,6,FSE Water said despite producing an
OL,7,Fadditional 100 million litres a day,
OL,8,Fdemand for drinking water needs to be
OL,9,Freduced to ensure that supply
OL,10,Finterruptions are not experienced
OL,11,Facross its network throughout the
OL,12,Fsummer.
OL,14,FThames Water, Britain's biggest water
OL,15,Fservices provider, told ITV News it
OL,16,Fhasn't introduced a hosepipe ban
OL,17,Fdespite recently boosting supply by
OL,18,Fone billion litres to its 16 million
OL,19,Fcustomers in London and the Thames
OL,20,FValley.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/15
