OL,3,CHosepipe ban: What you need to know as
OL,4,Chot weather leads to restrictions
OL,6,FThe company encouraged householders to
OL,7,Fmake small changes, such as fixing
OL,8,Fleaks, turning off taps when brushing
OL,9,Fteeth, using watering cans instead of
OL,10,Fhosepipes and sprinklers, and tending
OL,11,Fto gardens early in the morning or
OL,12,Flate in the evening.
OL,14,FWhat do you need to know about a
OL,15,Fhosepipe ban?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/15
