OL,3,CHosepipe ban: What you need to know as
OL,4,Chot weather leads to restrictions
OL,6,FWho has to comply?
OL,8,FYou are only at risk of prosecution if
OL,9,Fthe ban is in place where you live.
OL,11,FWho is exempt from a hosepipe ban?
OL,13,FPeople who are registered disabled,
OL,14,Fblue badge holders or those on a water
OL,15,Fcompanies' priority services register
OL,16,Fare among few exemptions.
OL,18,FBusinesses where a hosepipe is
OL,19,Fessential and ponds for the welfare of
OL,20,Ffish or aquatic animals are not
OL,21,Fincluded.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
