OL,3,CHosepipe ban: What you need to know as
OL,4,Chot weather leads to restrictions
OL,6,FNeither are pools required for medical
OL,7,Ftreatment and ornamental fountains
OL,8,Fthat are used for religious purposes.
OL,10,FHow can I water my garden?
OL,12,FWater companies advise watering plants
OL,13,Fwith a can or bucket.
OL,15,FEven during a ban, the use of a
OL,16,Fhosepipe for some gardening activities
OL,17,Fsuch as food crops in allotments or
OL,18,Fhome gardens, if they cannot
OL,19,Freasonably be watered with a watering
OL,20,Fcan, is still allowed.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/15
