OL,3,CHosepipe ban: What you need to know as
OL,4,Chot weather leads to restrictions
OL,6,FAndrew Tucker, of Thames Water, said:
OL,7,F"We can't do this alone.
OL,9,F"It's important that customers and
OL,10,Fbusinesses work with us to save water
OL,11,Fwhere they can and play their part in
OL,12,Fprotecting our vital resources."
OL,14,FA spokesman for Anglian Water, which
OL,15,Fhas six million customers in the East
OL,16,Fof England, added: "We have no plans
OL,17,Fto introduce a hosepipe ban this year.
OL,26,@oD@AOUqD@AOUtD@`O]xD@TOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31709
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1782442073
OL,3,CHosepipe ban: What you need to know as
OL,4,Chot weather leads to restrictions
OL,6,F"But during this current heatwave,
OL,7,Fwe're having to produce more water
OL,8,Fthan ever before to keep everyone on
OL,9,Fsupply, so we'd urge customers to
OL,10,Favoid using hosepipes and use less
OL,11,Fwater wherever they can.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
