OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31710
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1782442073
OL,3,CHosepipe ban: What you need to know as
OL,4,Chot weather leads to restrictions
OL,6,F"We recognise that water plays an
OL,7,Fimportant part in keeping cool and
OL,8,Fstaying hydrated during the heat, but
OL,9,Fanywhere you can cut back - for
OL,10,Finstance, by reusing water from
OL,11,Fpaddling pools to water your garden,
OL,12,Ftaking shorter showers or putting off
OL,13,Fnon-essential tasks like washing the
OL,14,Fcar - will make a significant
OL,15,Fdifference over the coming days."
