OL,3,CHosepipe ban: What you need to know as
OL,4,Chot weather leads to restrictions
OL,6,FAffinity Water serves 3.9 million
OL,7,Fpeople in parts of Bedfordshire,
OL,8,FBerkshire, Buckinghamshire, Essex,
OL,9,FHertfordshire, Surrey, and parts of
OL,10,FHarrow, Hillingdon, Barnet, Brent,
OL,11,FEaling and Enfield in London.
OL,13,FIt said it is not currently
OL,14,Fconsidering water use restrictions for
OL,15,Fcustomers across its supply area,
OL,16,Fincluding the Dour region, covering
OL,17,FFolkestone and Dover.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/15
