OL,3,CHosepipe ban: What you need to know as
OL,4,Chot weather leads to restrictions
OL,6,FA spokeswoman said: "With warmer
OL,7,Fweather comes naturally higher demand,
OL,8,Fand we're asking customers to use
OL,9,Fwater wisely this summer and avoid
OL,10,Funnecessary use, particularly while
OL,11,Fthe hot weather continues.
OL,13,F"We're monitoring the network
OL,14,Fcontinuously as part of our ongoing
OL,15,Fcommitment to maintaining a reliable
OL,16,Fsupply."
OL,18,FDavid Hinton, CEO of South East Water,
OL,19,Fsaid: "We completely understand why
OL,20,Feveryone reaches for the hose when the
OL,21,Fweather gets this hot.
OL,26,@nD@UOUuD@AOUxD@HO]{D@GOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31713
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1782442073
OL,3,CHosepipe ban: What you need to know as
OL,4,Chot weather leads to restrictions
OL,6,F"It's natural to want to enjoy our
OL,7,Fgardens and cool down, and we know how
OL,8,Ffrustrating it is to hear that
OL,9,Frestrictions are coming into place.
OL,11,F"Our teams have worked incredibly hard
OL,12,Fto prepare for this summer, but the
OL,13,Fsheer scale of this sustained heatwave
OL,14,Fmeans drinking water is being drawn
OL,15,Ffrom our storage tanks faster than it
OL,16,Fcan be treated and refilled.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31714
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1782442073
OL,3,CHosepipe ban: What you need to know as
OL,4,Chot weather leads to restrictions
OL,6,F"Our absolute priority has to be
OL,7,Fmaking sure there is always enough
OL,8,Fwater for everyone's essential daily
OL,9,Fneeds`like hygiene, drinking and
OL,10,Fcooking`and that we protect our
OL,11,Fvulnerable customers.
OL,13,F"To safeguard that shared supply and
OL,14,Fprevent any homes from facing a sudden
OL,15,Floss of water, we sadly need to ask
OL,16,Four communities to not use their
OL,17,Fhosepipes immediately.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31715
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1782442073
OL,3,CHosepipe ban: What you need to know as
OL,4,Chot weather leads to restrictions
OL,6,F"We are deeply sorry for the
OL,7,Fdisruption this causes, and we are
OL,8,Fincredibly grateful to everyone
OL,9,Fhelping us protect Kent's water."
